---
---

<main class="page">
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="brand">NEXOR</div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#signals">Signals</a>
      <a href="#operators">Operators</a>
      <a href="#bridge">AXYRO Bridge</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="signal-label">
      <span></span>
      Signal Layer / Future Gaming & Compute Culture
    </div>

    <h1>
      Future Gaming<br />
      & Compute Signals
    </h1>

    <p>
      Tracking the culture around future systems, sharper setups,
      software, hardware and digital environments.
    </p>
	

  <div class="hero-actions">
  <a href="#signals">Explore Signals</a>
  <a href="#bridge" class="ghost">AXYRO Bridge</a>
</div>

<div class="signal-lines">
  <span></span>
  <span></span>
  <span></span>
</div>
</section>
 <section id="signals" class="cards">
  <article class="featured">
    <span>01 / Future Setups</span>
    <h2>Clean machines.<br />Sharper environments.</h2>
    <p>
      NEXOR tracks the shift away from loud gaming rooms toward
      focused operator-grade setups and calmer digital workspaces.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article>
    <span>02 / Software Critique</span>
    <h2>Most software became louder than useful.</h2>
    <p>
      Interfaces are becoming noisy. NEXOR follows the tools that
      reduce friction instead of adding more.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="tall">
    <span>03 / Compute Culture</span>
    <h2>The next gaming culture is not RGB.</h2>
    <p>
      Future gaming is moving toward cleaner systems, calmer
      environments and sharper taste.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="wide">
    <span>04 / Signal Layer</span>
    <h2>
      Hardware.<br />
      Interfaces.<br />
      Operator culture.
    </h2>
  </article>
</section>

  <section id="operators" class="feed">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Operator Environments</p>
      <h2>Signal over noise.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="feed-grid">
      <div>Hardware Radar</div>
      <div>Interface Studies</div>
      <div>Setup Culture</div>
      <div>Weird Tech</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stream">
  <div class="stream-header">
    <p>Live Signal Stream</p>
    <h2>
      Tracking the shift toward calmer,
      sharper and more focused systems.
    </h2>
  </div>

  <div class="stream-grid">
    <article class="stream-card large">
      <span>SETUP CULTURE</span>
      <h3>Gaming rooms are slowly becoming operator environments.</h3>
    </article>

    <article class="stream-card">
      <span>INTERFACE SIGNAL</span>
      <h3>Most modern software mistakes noise for innovation.</h3>
    </article>

    <article class="stream-card">
      <span>HARDWARE RADAR</span>
      <h3>Future setups will feel calmer, darker and more intentional.</h3>
    </article>

    <article class="stream-card wide-card">
      <span>FUTURE COMPUTE</span>
      <h3>
        NEXOR tracks hardware, software and digital environments moving
        beyond overstimulated gaming culture.
      </h3>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

  <section id="bridge" class="bridge">
    <p>AXYRO builds the environment.</p>
    <h2>NEXOR tracks the signal around it.</h2>
  </section>
</main>

<style>
  :global(*) {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    background: #050608;
    color: #f5f7fa;
    font-family:
      Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
      "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
  }

  .page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 18%, rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.13), transparent 28%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 15% 85%, rgba(90, 120, 255, 0.08), transparent 32%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #050608 0%, #071016 48%, #050608 100%);
  }

  .page::before {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 64px 64px;
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, black 18%, black 72%, transparent);
    opacity: 0.18;
  }

  .page::after {
  content: "";
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  background:
    linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent 0%,
      rgba(183,255,60,0.025) 48%,
      transparent 100%
    ),
    radial-gradient(
      circle at 72% 22%,
      rgba(183,255,60,0.10),
      transparent 22%
    );
  opacity: 0.9;
  mix-blend-mode: screen;
}
  .nav {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 28px 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .brand {
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.56);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .hero {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 130px 0 110px;
	overflow: hidden;
  }

  .signal-label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.58);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .signal-label span {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #b7ff3c;
    box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.75);
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(58px, 9vw, 132px);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.075em;
    font-weight: 760;
  }

  .hero p {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.62);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    margin-top: 38px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .hero-actions a {
    padding: 13px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #b7ff3c;
    color: #050608;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .hero-actions .ghost {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.045);
    color: rgba(245,247,250,0.82);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  .cards {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 14px;
  padding-bottom: 110px;
}

 article {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  min-height: 260px;
  padding: 28px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  background:
    linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.06),
      rgba(255,255,255,0.018)
    ),
    #0b1016;
  border-radius: 28px;
  box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
}

article::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(
      circle at top right,
      rgba(183,255,60,0.08),
      transparent 36%
    );
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.45s ease;
}

article:hover::before {
  opacity: 1;
}

  article span {
    color: #b7ff3c;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.13em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  article h2 {
    margin: 46px 0 0;
    font-size: 26px;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  article p {
    margin-top: 18px;
    color: rgba(245,247,250,0.54);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .feed {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr;
    gap: 44px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: #b7ff3c;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .feed h2,
  .bridge h2 {
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 86px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.065em;
  }

  .feed-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .feed-grid div {
    min-height: 110px;
    padding: 22px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: #10161d;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    color: rgba(245,247,250,0.72);
  }

  .bridge {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 110px 0 140px;
  }

  .bridge p {
    color: rgba(245,247,250,0.55);
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .nav-links {
      display: none;
    }

    .hero {
      padding-top: 90px;
    }

    .cards,
    .feed {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    article {
      min-height: 230px;
    }

    .feed-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .featured {
  grid-column: span 2;
  min-height: 340px;
}

.featured h2 {
  font-size: 54px;
  max-width: 540px;
}

.tall {
  min-height: 340px;
}

.wide {
  grid-column: span 2;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  background:
    linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(183,255,60,0.08),
      rgba(255,255,255,0.02)
    ),
    #10161d;
}

.wide h2 {
  max-width: 620px;
  font-size: 58px;
  line-height: 0.92;
}

@media (max-width: 820px) {
  .cards {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .featured,
  .wide {
    grid-column: span 1;
  }

  .featured h2,
  .wide h2 {
    font-size: 42px;
  }
}
.signal-lines {
  position: absolute;
  top: 120px;
  right: -120px;
  width: 540px;
  height: 540px;
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 0.35;
}

.signal-lines span {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  border: 1px solid rgba(183,255,60,0.08);
  border-radius: 50%;
}

.signal-lines span:nth-child(1) {
  transform: scale(1);
}

.signal-lines span:nth-child(2) {
  transform: scale(1.22);
}

.signal-lines span:nth-child(3) {
  transform: scale(1.44);
}

.stream {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 40px 0 120px;
}

.stream-header {
  max-width: 760px;
}

.stream-header p {
  color: #b7ff3c;
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.stream-header h2 {
  margin-top: 18px;
  font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 76px);
  line-height: 0.96;
  letter-spacing: -0.06em;
}

.stream-grid {
  margin-top: 52px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
  gap: 14px;
}

.stream-card {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  min-height: 220px;
  padding: 28px;
  border-radius: 28px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  background:
    linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.055),
      rgba(255,255,255,0.02)
    ),
    #0b1016;
}

.stream-card::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(
      circle at top right,
      rgba(183,255,60,0.08),
      transparent 34%
    );
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
}

.stream-card:hover::before {
  opacity: 1;
}

.stream-card span {
  color: #b7ff3c;
  font-size: 12px;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.stream-card h3 {
   margin-top: 42px;
  max-width: 520px;
  font-size: 34px;
  line-height: 1.02;
  letter-spacing: -0.05em;
}
.stream-card.large {
  min-height: 320px;
}



.wide-card {
  grid-column: span 2;
  min-height: 220px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  background:
    linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(183,255,60,0.06),
      rgba(255,255,255,0.02)
    ),
    #10161d;
}

.wide-card h3 {
  max-width: 900px;
  font-size: 42px;
}

@media (max-width: 820px) {
  .stream-grid {
    margin-top: 52px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
  gap: 14px;
  align-items: stretch;
  }
}
</style>